# .gitignore for the com.luthien.box3d-unity package repo.
#
# This is a bare Unity *package* (package.json at the repo root), not a full
# Unity project — so there is no Library/, Temp/, Logs/, or Build/ to ignore.
#
# Intentionally TRACKED (do not add rules that would exclude these):
#   - *.meta                       Unity asset GUIDs — required, must be committed
#   - Runtime/Plugins/**/*.dll     shipped Windows x64 native binary
#   - Runtime/Plugins/**/*.so      shipped Linux x64 native binary
#   - Native~/                     build scripts (Unity ignores ~ folders; git should not)

# --- OS cruft ---
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- IDE / editor ---
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# --- Stray C#/.NET build output (only appears if the package is compiled
#     outside Unity, e.g. `dotnet build`; never committed) ---
obj/
bin/
*.csproj
*.sln
*.user

# --- Local native build intermediates, in case a build is ever pointed
#     at the package tree instead of a temp dir (see Native~/*.sh|*.bat) ---
Native~/build/
Native~/box3d-src/
